春节假期期间，受益于人口流动少、假期延长等因素，疫情扩散暂时局限在各地较小范围内。
During the Spring Festival, the spread of the epidemic was temporarily limited to a small geographical area, benefiting from factors such as low population movements and extended holidays.
特别是2月3日以来，除湖北以外全国每日新增确诊病例数持续下降，显示出疫情得到初步控制的积极信号。
In particular, since 3 February, the number of newly confirmed cases per day has continued to decline throughout the country, with the exception of Hubei, indicating a positive sign that the outbreak has been brought under initial control.
但是，随着2月10日全国陆续开始复工，春节后人口开始大规模回流，疫情传播范围将会扩大，这种“二次传播”可能加大疫情控制难度，需要高度警惕。
However, with the resumption of work nationwide on February 10 and the large-scale return of population after the Spring Festival, the spread of the epidemic will expand. This "secondary transmission" may make it more difficult to control the epidemic and requires a high degree of vigilance.
当前须重点关注接收武汉人口较多的两类区域，一是湖北省，二是河南、湖南、安徽、江西等周边省市（下文简称“周边四省”）。
Attention must now be focused on the two major population-receiving regions of Wuhan, namely Hubei Province and the neighboring provinces of Henan, Hunan, Anhui and Jiangxi (hereinafter referred to as the "four neighboring provinces").
由于湖北全省已采取有力隔离措施，人口流出少，“二次传播”基本被阻断。
As Hubei Province has taken strong isolation measures, the outflow of population is small, "secondary transmission" was basically blocked.
周边四省既是武汉回流人口大省，也是北上广深回流人口大省，是“二次传播”的主渠道。
The four neighboring provinces are not only the province of returning population in Wuhan, but also the province of returning population in the north, which is the main channel of "secondary transmission."
从全国人口流动总体情况看，我国劳务输出主要有四大通道，分别是河南-三大都市圈、安徽-长三角、湖南湖北江西-珠三角、河北-京津。
From the overall situation of population movement, China's labor export mainly has four major channels, namely Henan-three metropolitan circles, Anhui-Yangtze River Delta, Hunan Hubei Jiangxi-Pearl River Delta, Hebei-Jingjin.
除河北外，其他劳务输出大省都在湖北周边。
Except Hebei province, other labor export provinces are around Hubei.
春节后这些省的外出人口，可能成为疫情向大城市蔓延的重要途径。
The out-migration of these provinces after the Spring Festival may become an important way to spread the epidemic to large cities.
正月是人口返城回流集中期，从往年看，这一过程将持续到元宵节后十天左右，预计今年将会进一步延迟。
In previous years, this process will last about 10 days after the Lantern Festival. Further delays are expected this year.
从流出角度看，2019年正月1日至24日之间，河南、湖南、安徽、江西的跨省流出人口总量分别达1400万、1100万、1300万、900万人（注释[3]），大部分流向大都市圈。
In terms of outflow, between January 1 and 24 2019, the total inter-provincial outflow from Henan, Hunan, Anhui, and Jiangxi totaled 14 million, 11, 13 million, and 9 million, respectively (Refer. & # 91; 3 & # 93; & # 93;), mostly to the metropolitan area.
具体来看，河南流向京津冀、长三角、珠三角城市的人数都较多，包括北京（104万）、上海（72万）、苏州（71万）、杭州（41万）、深圳（36万）、东莞（31万）、广州（31万）、宁波（27万）。
Specifically, Henan flows to the cities of Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei, Yangtze River Delta and Pearl River Delta, including Beijing (1.04 million), Shanghai (0.72 million), Suzhou (710,000), Hangzhou (410,000), Shenzhen (360,000), Dongguan (310,000), Guangzhou (310,000) and Ningbo (270,000).
湖南外出人口主要流向珠三角，包括广州（126万）、深圳（113万）、东莞（109万）、佛山（47万）、清远（37万）、中山（28万）、惠州（25万）。
The majority of Hunan emigrants to the Pearl River Delta include Guangzhou (1.26 million), Shenzhen (1.13 million), Dongguan (1.09 million), Foshan (470,000), Qingyuan (370,000), Zhongshan (280,000) and Huizhou (250,000).
安徽外出人口主要流向长三角，包括上海（180万）、南京（133万）、苏州（110万）、杭州（85万）、宁波（54万）、无锡（50万）、徐州（49万）。
Anhui emigrated mainly to the Yangtze River Delta, including Shanghai (1.8 million), Nanjing (1.33 million), Suzhou (1.1 million), Hangzhou (850,000), Ningbo (540,000), Wuxi (500,000) and Xuzhou (490,000).
江西主要外出人口主要流向珠三角和长三角，包括深圳（67万）、广州（53万）、杭州（48万）、东莞（45万）、上海（44万）、温州（35万）、泉州（30万）。
The majority of the migrant population in Jiangxi mainly flows to the Pearl River Delta and the Yangtze River Delta, including Shenzhen (670,000), Guangzhou (530,000), Hangzhou (480,000), Dongguan (450,000), Shanghai (440,000), Wenzhou (350,000) and Quanzhou (300,000).
此外，2019年湖北跨省流出人口总量为900万人，预计今年仍将保持这一规模，但由于目前湖北交通封闭而暂时处于隔离状态。
In addition, the population outflow from Hubei Province, totalling 9 million in 2019, is expected to remain so this year, but is temporarily isolated due to the current traffic closure in Hubei Province.
图4 春节后河南流出人口去向及数量：主要大城市数据来源：百度公司图5 春节后湖南流出人口去向及数量：主要大城市数据来源：百度公司图6 春节后安徽流出人口去向及数量：主要大城市数据来源：百度公司图7 春节后江西流出人口去向及数量：主要大城市数据来源：百度公司大城市在春节后面临人口返城高峰期，疫情防控压力将会明显加大。
2007-9-25 21: 48 Data on the outflow from Anhui after the Spring Festival: Data on the outflow from Anhui after the Spring Festival: Data on the outflow from Jiangxi after the Spring Festival: Data on the outflow of population from Jiangxi after the Spring Festival.
从流入角度看，2019年正月1日至24日之间，北京、上海、广州、深圳的流入人口总量分别达1300万、1100万、530万、570万人，其中来自河南、湖南、安徽、江西四省合计分别占13%、29%、41%、40%，如果再加上湖北则分别占15%、32%、52%、51%。
In terms of inflow, between January 1 and 24, 2019, the inflow to Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou and Shenzhen totaled 13 million, 11 million, 5.3 million and 5.7 million respectively, with the provinces of Henan, Hunan, Anhui and Jiangxi accounting for 13%, 29%, 41% and 40% respectively, with Hubei accounting for 15%, 32%, 52% and 51% respectively.
广州、深圳等珠三角城市约一半外来人口来自湖北及周边四省，随着企业陆续复工，疫情加剧的可能性很大。
About half of the migrant population in Guangzhou, Shenzhen and other Pearl River Delta cities come from Hubei and the surrounding provinces.
往年经验显示，自然状态下的节后人口流动在时间上高度集中，主要集中在假期结束的前后三天。
Experience in previous years has shown that post-holiday movements under natural conditions are highly concentrated in time, mainly three days before and after the end of the holiday period.
今年由于春节假期推迟一周，人口流动高峰期也将随之延迟。
This year's peak migration will be delayed by a week's postponement of the Spring Festival holiday.
在人口集中流动时期，高铁、飞机等交通工具成为各路人群汇集场所，大大增加了病毒传染的概率。
During the period of concentrated population movement, high-speed rail and airplane transportation means become the meeting place of all kinds of people, greatly increasing the probability of virus transmission.
三、分区分业分步复工当前疫情防控形势严峻，节后人口大规模返城、企业复工、气温转暖等因素，可能进一步加剧疫情。
The current situation of epidemic prevention and control is very serious, and factors such as the large-scale return of population after the holidays, the resumption of work by enterprises and the warming of temperatures may further aggravate the epidemic.
疫情重点区域将会扩大，从湖北及其周围省市，转向三大都市圈和沿海发达省市。
The key areas of the epidemic will be expanded from Hubei and its surrounding provinces to the three metropolitan areas and developed coastal provinces and cities.
判断疫情演变形势，明确防控重点，对于增强战胜疫情信心、提升防控效果至关重要。
Judging the evolution of the epidemic situation, clear priorities for prevention and control, to strengthen confidence in overcoming the epidemic, improve the effectiveness of prevention and control.
为此，提出以下政策建议。
To this end, the following policy recommendations are made.
一是进一步阻断疫情“二次传播”渠道。
One is to further block the "secondary transmission" of the epidemic.
当前，湖北省人口流出已得到严格控制，但周边四省人口流出仍然较多，是疫情输出的重要隐患。
At present, the outflow of population from Hubei Province has been strictly controlled, but the outflow from the surrounding four provinces is still relatively high.
应以河南、湖南、安徽、江西等劳务输出大省为防控重点，考虑进一步延后或分散上述省市人口集中外流。
Henan, Hunan, Anhui, Jiangxi and other large labor export provinces should be the focus of prevention and control, consider further delay or disperse the concentration of the above-mentioned provinces and cities.
上述四省中，人口输出较多的城市是防控关键，主要包括郑州（390万）、周口（350万）、长沙（340万）、合肥（310万）、阜阳（290万）、商丘（270万）、上饶（240万）、驻马店（240万）、衡阳（240万）、南阳（240万）、宿州（230万）、邵阳（220万）、信阳（220万）、亳州（210万）、赣州（210万）。
Among the four provinces, cities with high population export are key to control, including Zhengzhou (3.9 million), Zhoukou (3.5 million), Changsha (3.4 million), Hefei (3.1 million), Fuyang (2.9 million), Shang Qiu (2.7 million), Shang Rao (2.4 million), Ma Tan (2.4 million), Nanyang (2.4 million), Suzhou (2.3 million), Shaoyang (2.2 million), Bozhou (2.2 million), Bozhou (2.1 million) and Ganzhou (2.1 million).
（注释[4]）要压实地方政府责任，在人口流出地环节加强疫情筛查。
(Refer to & # 91; 4 & # 93; & # 93; & # 93; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 45;
二是加强防人口流入城市的防控力度。
Second, strengthen the prevention and control of population flow to cities.
对北上广深等特大城市，春节后返城的“二次传播”人数，是春节前来自武汉“一次传播”人数的30-60倍（注释[5]），疫情防控压力更大。
At 30 to 60 times the number of people from Wuhan who returned to the city after the Spring Festival, the number of people returning to the city after the Spring Festival is 30 to 60 times greater than the number at once from Wuhan (Refer to & # 91; # 91; 5; # 93; & # 93; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 45; & nbsp; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
除湖北以外其他省市2月10日已开始复工，人口大量集中返城，输入型扩散难以避免，这对原有的防控体系和防控能力形成巨大挑战。
With the exception of Hubei province, where work resumed on February 10, the population returned to the cities in large numbers, making it difficult to avoid imported proliferation, posing a huge challenge to the original control system and prevention and control capacity.
大城市既要防输入，更要防扩散。
Large cities should be protected against both import and proliferation.
对策是加强源头管理，强化对来自湖北及周边四省人员的检疫，利用大数据工具精准掌握人员流向。
The countermeasure is to strengthen the source management, strengthen the quarantined personnel from Hubei and the surrounding four provinces, and use big data tools to accurately grasp the flow of personnel.
加强早期识别，严格筛查疑似病例，分级分类进行隔离。
Strengthening early identification, strict screening of suspected cases, classification for isolation.
同时，增加应急医疗服务供给，加快建设集中隔离点，集中收治疑似病例，减少居家隔离带来的家庭和社区传染。
At the same time, increase the supply of emergency medical services, speed up the construction of centralized isolation points, centralize the treatment of suspected cases, and reduce family and community transmission from home isolation.
划小隔离单元，切断传染源与外界联系。
Small isolation unit, cut off the source of infection with the outside world.
完善信息披露，减少社会恐慌心理。
Perfect information disclosure, reduce social panic psychology.
三是分地区分行业分步骤推动企业灵活复工，掌握疫情防控和保增长、保障物资供应之间的平衡。
Thirdly, the enterprises should be encouraged to return to work flexibly by sub-sectors to master the balance between disease prevention and control, maintenance of growth and supply of materials.
原则上，以外来人员就业为主的地区，应适当延迟复工，以本地人员就业为主的地区，应视条件优先复工。
In principle, the resumption of work in areas dominated by the employment of foreign personnel shall be delayed appropriately, and in areas where employment of local personnel is the mainstay, priority shall be given to resuming work.
适当延迟劳动密集型行业复工，优先放宽非劳动密集型行业复工。
We will delay the resumption of labor-intensive industries and give priority to reactivating non-labor-intensive industries.
重点保障疫情防控必需、城市运行必需、群众生活必需的行业。
Key to ensure the prevention and control of epidemic diseases, urban operational necessities, essential industries.
建立企业复工报备制度，对企业疫情防控措施开展必要的评估。
To establish a system for the re-entry of workers to carry out necessary evaluation of enterprise disease prevention and control measures.
鼓励复工企业根据不同岗位特征，采取远程办公或弹性上班制，分散上下班时间，平抑城市内通勤高峰。
Restart-to-work enterprises are encouraged to adopt telecommuting or flex-time to spread their time to and from work, according to the characteristics of their positions.
注释：[1]以农历腊月29日（公历1月23日）武汉“封城”为界，2020年春节人口流动可分为两个阶段。
Note: & # 91; & # 93; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 39; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 39; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & #
在此之前，全国每日人口流动的时空态势与2019年高度一致；在此之后与2019年存在明显不同，主要原因是疫情加重、信息广泛传播、假期延长、居民主动减少外出等因素，导致人口流动特征发生较大变化，劳动力返城明显延迟。
Until then, the spatial and temporal dynamics of daily population movements in the country were highly consistent with 2019, which was significantly different from 2019, mainly due to factors such as an increase in the epidemic, widespread dissemination of information, longer holidays and a reduction in absenteeism of the population, leading to greater changes in the characteristics of population movements and significant delays in returning to the cities.
[2]根据百度数据，进入腊月后，我国每日流动人口约1600万人，武汉占全国流动人口比重为1.5%。
According to Baidu, China's migrant population was about 16 million a day after entering the month, with Wuhan accounting for 1.5% of the nation's migrant population.
[3]上述数字不含省内流动人口。
The above figures do not include provincial migrants.
[4]括号内数字为该市2019年正月1日至24日的人口流出总规模。
The figures in parentheses represent the total size of the city's outflows from 1 to 24 January 2019.
[5]根据前文测算，春节前武汉流入北上广深的人数分别约6.3万、5.3万、3.8万、3.6万。
According to previous calculations, Wuhan accounted for about 63,000, 53,000, 38,000 and 36,000 people entering northern Shangdong before the Spring Festival.
春节后湖北周边四省流入北上广深的人数分别约170万、320万、220万、230万。
After the Spring Festival, about 1.7 million people, 3.2 million people, 2.2 million people and 2.3 million people flowed into the northern part of Hubei province.
作者为国务院发展研究中心副研究员，编辑：马克责编 | 蒋丽lijiang@caijing.com.cn。
The writer is a associate researcher at the Development Research Center of the State Council. Editor: Mark & # 124; Jiang Lijiang @ caijing.com.cn.
